snippet.title: JUMP FORCE - Seto Kaiba DLC Trailer | X1, PS4, PC
snippet.description:
The "Number 1 Ranked Duelist in the country" is making his way to the JUMP FORCE Character Pass in May! Catch a first look at Seto Kaiba gameplay with Blue-Eyes White Dragon & Obelisk the Tormentor. 

Order the #JUMPFORCE Character Pass today: https://bandainam.co/JumpForcePO
